climbs.name: May the Force Be With You

content.description:
A small tree grows under the left side of the Darth Vader Dome.  May the Force Be With You begins just left of this tree, at a small crack with rust colorations. 

  Start towards the bottom of a right-leaning notch, and work your way up through the dihedryl and textured crack-and-flake system to the top.
Han Solo follows the short crack to the right of the main face of Darth Vader Dome.
content.protection: Short, bouldery problem.  bring a pad.

content.description:
Chewbacca begins 15 feet right of May the Force Be With You, at the base of the longest white-quartz streak in the face, under the lowest roof. 

  Start on the slick face and through the lowest roof, then trend right to gain a large bucket on the outside corner.
content.protection: Toprope only, access from the top.

content.description: The Darth Vader Dome is a short section of rock on the southern tip of Wolf Rock.  Facing west, this dome-shaped section vaguely resembles the eponymous villainâ€™s helmet.  Some of Wolf Rock's hardest routes are here, especially in the center of the overhung face.
